            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Version 1.7.5 — Story Info & Release Notes</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>New:</strong> Story Info now shows which AI created your story — see the text and image providers at a glance</li>
  <li><strong>New:</strong> See the image prompt for the page you're reading in Story Info</li>
  <li><strong>New:</strong> AI provider and model details are saved with each storybook</li>
  <li><strong>Improved:</strong> Update dialog now shows what's new in each version</li>
</ul>]]></description>
